The paper deals with the analysis of time series data, which is a common topic in database research (cs.DB). The use of SVD for dimensionality reduction and pattern discovery is also relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Finally, the paper proposes a new method for efficiently computing SVD for a given time range query, which could be of interest to researchers in data structures (cs.DS).
